VSo, my mother's a pediatrician,
p4
aVand when I was young, she'd tell the craziest stories
p5
aVthat combined science with her overactive imagination.
p6
aVOne of the stories she told was that if you eat a lot of salt,
p7
aVall of the blood rushes up your legs,
p8
aVthrough your body,
p9
aVand shoots out the top of your head,
p10
aVkilling you instantly.
p11
